stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> LegacyOnly : start here
    LegacyOnly --> DualCompute : new path added,\nboth compute
    DualCompute --> ProgressiveCutover : parity ≥ 99.99%
    ProgressiveCutover --> EventDriven : all capabilities cut over
    EventDriven --> LegacyRetired : legacy path removed
    LegacyRetired --> [*]

    note right of DualCompute
        Legacy path: sole production writer
        New path: computes but does not apply
        Parity is measured, not assumed
    end note

    note right of ProgressiveCutover
        One capability at a time
        Rollback = flip one flag
        No big-bang cutover
    end note
